WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.370
Ushbu mashqda sikl va turtle lar haqida bilgan narsalaringizdan foydalanib

00:00:05.370 --> 00:00:07.155
o‘zingizning biror narsangizni chizishingizni xohlaymiz.

00:00:07.155 --> 00:00:10.920
Ammo, aniqrog‘i, biz sizga kamalak ranglarining ro‘yxatini berdik

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:14.775
va biz sizga kamalak ranglarida biron bir narsa chizishingizni istardik.

00:00:14.775 --> 00:00:19.685
Turli xil rangli qirralar bilan shakl chizish uchun siz ushbu ro‘yxat bo‘yicha sikldan foydalanishingiz mumkin.

00:00:19.685 --> 00:00:24.010
Bu yerda siz bunday sikl bilan yaratishingiz mumkin bo‘lgan shakllarning bir nechta namunalari.

00:00:24.010 --> 00:00:26.070
Siz shunchaki tomonlari har xil rangda bo‘lgan oltiburchak

00:00:26.070 --> 00:00:28.290
chizishingiz mumkin,

00:00:28.290 --> 00:00:30.750
yoki biroz vaqt sarflab, 

00:00:30.750 --> 00:00:34.335
kamalakni chizishingiz yoki umuman boshqa narsani qilishingiz mumkin.

00:00:34.335 --> 00:00:38.800
Uni sinab ko‘rganingizdan so‘ng ikkalasiga ham sizga kodni ko‘rsatamiz.

